{"tid":1992492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【害撚死】東京奧組委主席稱若疫情明年前未受控 奧運將取消","createTime":"2020-04-28T07:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T10:36:56.000Z","uid":37661,"like":79,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"c8bbe4bc0301dd5b866c0cf0fe76e4975b3a50a2","tid":1992492,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:33:00.000Z","msg":"東京奧組委主席稱若疫情明年前未受控 奧運將取消<br />\n2020-04-28 HKT 15:29<br />\n東京奧運組委會主席森喜朗說，若果新型冠狀病毒疫情到明年之前仍未受控，已經押後一年的東京奧運將會取消，不會再延期。<br />\n<br />\n因為疫情而要延期一年的東京奧運，定於明年7月23日開幕。森喜朗接受日本《體育日刊》訪問時說，若全球到時仍然無法走出疫情，奧運會將無法延至明年之後，在這種情況下，將要取消。<br />\n<br />\n另外，「日本醫師會」會長橫倉義武在記者會說，除非找到有效應對新型冠狀病毒的疫苗，否則東京奧運很難舉行，希望能加緊研發治療藥物和疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523184-20200428.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523184-20200428.htm&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPktrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=09daf64d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523184-20200428.htm&h=10e370d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523184-20200428.htm</a>"},{"pid":"311b56bca14d0a906e520a9ed1cef11f896bce07","tid":1992492,"uid":235316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:33:28.000Z","msg":"[行動po]香港人日程表更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"865a527b39ca547710d45a030c000657c393f62b","tid":1992492,"uid":104804,"like":71,"dislike":2,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:36:28.000Z","msg":"以後邊個搞奥運世界杯<br />\n支那一出病毒戰又win"},{"pid":"bf690a62150de724ec0ec7235f23ffe8dbc319c0","tid":1992492,"uid":37661,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"865a527b39ca547710d45a030c000657c393f62b","tid":1992492,"uid":104804,"like":71,"dislike":2,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:36:28.000Z","msg":"以後邊個搞奥運世界杯<br />\n支那一出病毒戰又win"